item.title: CVE-2023-35896|2024-08-02T16:37:39.912Z -- ibm -- content%20navigator
item.description: IBM Content Navigator 3.0.13 is vulnerable to server-side request forgery (SSRF). This may allow an authenticated attacker to send unauthorized requests from the system, potentially leading to network enumeration or facilitating other attacks. IBM X-Force ID: 259247.
